c: 5
v: 45
t: "Soni mwalakwemo twalamwile ŵanganyao yanti: “Mundu awulajidwe ligongo lya kuwulaga mundu, liso likolotoledwe ligongo lya kolotola liso, lupula lukatidwe ligongo lyakata lupula, liwiwi likatidwe ligongo lyakata liwiwi, lino likuulidwe ligongo lyakuula lino, nombe maŵanga gana mbusyo (syakwe).” Nambo jwaakululwiche yalakweyo mwasadaka, basi yele (yakululukayo) tiyintendekasye kululuchilidwa sambi syakwe, soni ŵangakwilanyichisya yaatulwisye Allah, basi ŵanganyao niŵali ŵalupuso"